            "Following are possible reasons that break CAPTCHA:"
            "and following are possible workarounds:"
            "Alternatively, you can also"
            "contact us"
            "and let us help you."
            ]
            reason: [
            "Browser extensions like Adblock may block CAPTCHA."
            "IP address from VPN may be used by bots before."
            ]
            workaround: [
            "Disable extensions by logging in with incognito mode.
            "Try again with different IP addresses.
            ["Login with", "this link", "which clear cookie for you."]
            "Check if you input correct and valid data."
            ]
            close: "Close This Popup"
          "zh-TW":
            title: "CAPTCHA Issue"
            desc: "真人驗證 (CAPTCHA) 失敗"
            p: [
            "您執行此動作時，程式需要執行真人驗證(CAPTCHA) ，但這個驗證失敗了；它可能是無法分辨您是否為真人，亦可能是完全無法執行。因此，您要求的動作沒有執行成功。"
            "以下是一些可能造成此問題的原因："
